    '1.0.0',
    'Structured vector similarity search for cargo consignment risk detection. Encodes each consignment as a semantically meaningful feature string from structured attributes (hs_chapter, origin_risk_tier, transport_code, value_per_kg range, is_disguise_category). Embeds via ONNX in-database. Scores against RiskProfile reference embeddings using TD_VectorDistance cosine. Produces similarity_score_max which feeds the Prediction module feature store.',
    'entity_embedding',
    'MEMORY, SEMANTIC, DOMAIN',
    'PREDICTION',
    'Australian Border Force Data Architecture',
    'CargoIntelligence Data Product Team',
    'DAILY',
    CURRENT_DATE,
