    'No parameters. Returns all active relationships across all modules. To render as Mermaid erDiagram: for each row emit {from_table} {cardinality_symbol} {to_table} : {relationship_desc}. Symbols: ONE_TO_ONE = ||--||, ONE_TO_MANY = ||--o{, MANY_TO_ONE = }o--||, MANY_TO_MANY = }o--o{.',
    'Lightweight query on a {{small_T}} metadata table. No performance concerns.',
